  <brief_title>Rasburicase for Treatment of Hyperuricemia in Children and Adolescence Patients With Tumor Lysis Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase IV, Compassionate Use Program of Rasburicase for Treatment of Hyperuricemia in Children and Adolescence Patients With Tumor Lysis Syndrome</official_title>
