  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To provide treatment opportunity to children and adolescent patients with hematologic
      malignancies by supplying the delayed marketed product and also to observe the efficacy and
      safety of rasburicase used in the treatment of hyperuricemia
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
